                    <li>
                        <p class="line-bold"><b>⦁	Energy Efficiency</b></p>
                        <p>In addition to their dynamic visual performance, <b>Direct View LED Video Walls</b> are more energy-efficient than conventional display technologies. <b>Direct View LED</b> displays offer a better eco-friendly resolution that lowers operating costs without compromising quality for large-scale events where energy consumption is a crisis.</p>
                    </li>
